platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: The Wizarding World springs to life in Harry Potter: Puzzles & Spells. Match your way through memorable moments—clearing puzzle boards of pesky trolls, chocolate frogs, and more—as you’re treated to gorgeous levels inspired by the beloved books and films. This best-in-class match-3’s most impressive bit of sorcery is conjuring up a distinct take on puzzle games—one that’s packed with spells, daily challenges, and collectible beasts. You’ll feel as powerful as Dumbledore himself.
